text: Sonja Čevnik (born 12 December 1990) is a Slovenian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Slovenia women's national team. ==Career== Čevnik has been capped for the Slovenia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian women's footballers Category:Slovenia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
